Update Utility 4.1.0.474 console version
(C) 2020 AO Kaspersky Lab
Usage: UpdateUtility-Console [<key>[=<value] [<key>...]]
Description: This program must be run in Unix-way (under user)

  -u,     --update                Perform update
  -c, -o, --configuration         Set configuration file name. By default using updater.ini
  -t,     --trace                 
  -d,     --dump                  Set dump enabled
  -s,     --silent                Set silent mode (no messages)
  -r,     --report                Enable report
          --accepteula            Accept EULA
          --acceptprivacypolicy   Accept Privacy Policy
          --acceptksn             Accept KSN
          --declineksn            Decline KSN
          --proxy_login           Proxy login
          --proxy_password        Proxy password
  -h,     --help                  Print this help.
